profile:
White Eagle Homes started in 1996, at a time when affordable housing was dull and unimaginative. We quickly made a name for ourselves with an emphasis on innovative design and Customer Satisfaction that would change the face of home building forever.

Custom building is our specialty; we are proud to offer our clients unique homes which we build to suit their unique requirements and match their lifestyles. White Eagle can also modify any of its existing plans in order to better suit your needs. Also, if you have an idea or sketch of your own we can make it a reality.

profile:
We create environments for amazing lives to happen.
From award-winning customer service to world-class home design, building a Cantiro home means you can expect more. 
Our homes are designed around life. It’s a thoughtful, understanding, and empathetic process that puts the life of our customer at the core of every decision. It’s a harmony of form and function, beauty and style. Your must-haves are just the beginning and we design beyond the essentials to deliver a higher quality of lifestyle.
We are part of Cantiro – a real estate company building homes, communities, commercial and residential rental properties. We are driven by innovation, passion, entrepreneurship and a commitment to doing the right thing for our customers, staff, partners and stakeholders.
Thank you to everyone who has taken the time to write a review. Each and every one provides valuable feedback on what we’re doing well and where we can improve. 
Please see all that we do at cantiro.ca
